data.description: 7715 Lakeshore Drive is a real estate gem located in the picturesque town of McCalla, Alabama. Lake living with all of the conveniences of city life! New paint, new bathrooms, new kitchen windows, new countertops, new carpet, newly encapsulated crawl space, new Pellicle Piers on back foundation to stabilize with a lifetime warranty and new pipe from road to meter. Perfect for a family moving within minutes of the new UAB Medical West hospital. Move in ready, motivated seller. Show anytime.
